name: Whitesnake
profile:
Hard Rock band (1978-1986, 1997-present) and Hair / Glam Metal (Heavy Metal) band (1987-1996) from London, England (United Kingdom).

Line-up 2021-present:
David Coverdale - Vocals
Joel Hoekstra- Guitar
Reb Beach - Guitar
Tanya O'Callaghan - Bass
Tommy Aldridge - Drums
Dino Jelusick - keyboards, vocals
Michele Luppi - Keyboard, backing vocals
